snippet.title: Penumbra Requiem
snippet.description:
Expansion for Penumbra: Black Plague. Epilogue to the Black Plague game, experimenting with physics puzzles and giving a tad more story to the Penumbra series for those eager to find all the answers.

http://www.penumbragame.com
